{"version":1,"entries":{"person_3116034_translations":{"at":1772647164985,"data":{"id":3116034,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"A rising South Korean actor and model belonging to the Namyang Hong clan. He is currently a student in the Acting Department at the Seoul Institute of the Arts and is managed by Fable Company. In 2019, he appeared in the Dingo Studio dating web variety show Lookating. He made his official acting debut in 2020 through the web drama 187cm 155cm and subsequently starred in several web series. In 2024, he made his first television appearance in the tvN drama Love on a Single Log Bridge. His notable works include The Love-Struck Thief and Study Group.","name":"Hong Min-gi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"대한민국의 신예 배우이자 모델로, 본관은 남양 홍씨이다. 현재 서울예술대학교 연기과에 재학 중이며, 소속사는 페이블컴퍼니(Fable Company)이다. 2019년 딩고 스튜디오(Dingo Studio)의 소개팅 웹 예능 ‘루카팅(Lookating)’에 출연했다. 2020년 웹드라마 ‘187cm 155cm’를 통해 배우로 정식 데뷔한 후 다수의 웹드라마에 출연했다. 2024년 tvN 드라마 ‘사랑은 외나무다리에서’에 출연하며 TV 드라마 신고식을 치렀다. 주요 출연작으로는 ‘은애하는 도적님’, ‘스터디그룹’ 등이 있다.","name":"홍민기","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"韩国新生代演员、模特，本贯南阳洪氏， 首尔艺术大学表演系在读，隶属于Fable Company。2019年，参加Dingo Studio推出的相亲网综《Lookating》。2020年，通过网剧《187cm 155cm》作为演员正式出道，随后拍摄多部网剧。2024年，参演tvN《爱在独木桥》建立知名度。代表作包括《恩爱的盗贼大人》、《流氓读书会》等。","name":"洪民基","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Hong Min Ki","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"韓國新生代演員、模特兒，本貫南陽洪氏，現就讀於首爾藝術大學表演系，隸屬於 Fable Company。2019 年，參加 Dingo Studio 推出的相親網綜《Lookating》。2020 年，透過網劇《187cm 155cm》作為演員正式出道，隨後拍攝多部網劇。2024 年，參演 tvN《愛在獨木橋》，首次在電視劇（無線/有線台）中亮相。代表作包括《恩愛的盜賊大人》、《流氓讀書會》等。","name":"洪民基","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"韓國新生代演員、模特兒，本貫南陽洪氏，現就讀於首爾藝術大學表演系，隸屬於 Fable Company。2019年，參加 Dingo Studio 推出的相親網綜《Lookating》。2020年，透過網劇《187cm 155cm》作為演員正式出道，隨後拍攝多部網劇。2024年，參演 tvN《愛在獨木橋》，首次在電視劇（無線/有線台）中亮相。代表作包括《恩愛的盜賊大人》、《流氓讀書會》等。","name":"洪民基","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SK","iso_639_1":"sk","name":"Slovenčina","english_name":"Slovak","data":{"biography":"","name":"Hong Min-gi","primary":false}}]}},"person_1343551_translations":{"at":1772647178370,"data":{"id":1343551,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Aom Phiyada Akkaraseranee is a Thai actress, model, and host. She is the second daughter of Pisarn Akarasenee, a well-known actor and producer of various popular Thai TV series.\n\nPhiyada Akkraseranee graduated with a Bachelor of Science degree in education from the Srinakharinwirot University in Bangkok. She began her career as a model for commercials on TV in 1996. Her first drama as the leading actress was \"Torfun and Marwin\" produced by Exact co.\n\nAom gained a lot of popular and talent Awards including Best Actress in Asian Television Awards. Meanwhile, Aom also became a hot host of variety talk shows for Wan Warn Yang Wharn You and E-mouth in 2004.\n\nAom married Art Sara Jutharattanakul in August 2009, and their wedding reception was held in October 2009. They have a daughter named Nava.","name":"Phiyada Jutharattanakul","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"พิยดา จุฑารัตนกุล","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"拼塔安·阿孔萨妮","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"拼塔安·阿孔薩妮","primary":false}}]}},"tv_249907_credits":{"at":1772647187633,"data":{"cast":[{"adult":fa